    Class Description
    ORMAbstractXYLayoutPolicy  
    ORMAttributeComponentEditPolicy
    This ComponentEditPolicy handels requests for the deletion of Attributes and returns and creats the deletion commands.
    ORMAttributeDirectEditPolicy
    This DirectEditPolicy shows DirectEdit feedback and creates the Command to perform a "direct edit" of a Attribute name.
    ORMCompartmentDiagramXYLayoutPolicy
    This XYLayoutEditPolicy handels request for creation and boundarie changes of Compartments, Groupings and NaturalTypes in a CompartmentDiagram and returns and creates the nessecary commands for the creation and boundarie change.

    This DirectEditPolicy shows DirectEdit feedback and creates the Command to perform a "direct edit" of a Method name.
    ORMNodeDirectEditPolicy
    This DirectEditPolicy shows DirectEdit feedback and creates the Command to perform a "direct edit" of a Node name.
    ORMNodeGraphicalNodeEditPolicy
    This GraphicalNodeEditPolicy handles request for the creations of all kinds of Relations and creates and returns the necessary commands for that purpose.
    ORMRelationBendpointEditPolicy

    ORMRelationConnectionEditPolicy
